{"tid":1329360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳同佳案，應該係政府急，泛民唔使幫政府解圍！","createTime":"2019-07-18T07:41:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T11:00:45.000Z","uid":237133,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8084c27de9e8e8d22743fc64ea74ac076ea9bd13","tid":1329360,"uid":237133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:41:58.000Z","msg":"政局變化一日都嫌多！<br />\n<br />\n陳同佳依家仲坐緊監，10月先至放出嚟！到時根本<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府比泛民建制仲要急！</span></span>一個政治炸彈，泛民到時睇情況先至出手咁先合理！<br />\n<br />\n我之前d post講過，目前應該集中五大訴求！(甚至應該集中一至兩個！)假設逃犯條例已dead(據林鄭所講)，就應該focus警權過大，改革警隊問題！進而要求<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全面政治改革！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n楊岳橋，尹兆堅同張超雄三個建議其實各有好處，理性d講就算立咗法，逃犯被&ldquo;送中&quot;嘅機會仍然係0，不過咁，政治就係perception is everything，唔該<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">三位議員高抬貴手！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n免得失焦，節外生枝，仲有被人覺得有分化嘅嫌疑！<br />\n<br />\n陳同佳嘅嘢，去到10月就會有solution，政府<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自己攞嚟衰</span></span>，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冇得唔拆彈</span></span>，到時會同建制，甚至可能加埋泛民，做場大龍鳳！我地平民百姓唔使操心！我地要focus番我地面對嘅問題！<br />\n<br />\n認同請推！"},{"pid":"06c48ed37f55dd9dfd6ec8253b89db1d92e1c7ff","tid":1329360,"uid":237133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:42:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"159e3826fc8eb34f1f3622267fcf7d3697615594","tid":1329360,"uid":237133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:44:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"534d318e135f7269ecdc620cc2ab4818ce53eb4f","tid":1329360,"uid":237133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:44:51.000Z","msg":"重要，要推"},{"pid":"f0e302f09196364bd5c9bc0ac3973a76593bc155","tid":1329360,"uid":119283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:19:10.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"04334329dda08287e8e2aecf43878d1daf9222b